== Description ==

The [[Image:Std_ToggleBottomPanels.svg|24px]] '''Std ToggleBottomPanels''' command toggles the visibility of the bottom panels (usually [[Report_View|Report View]] and [[Python_Console|Python Console]]).

== Usage ==

# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View →  [[Image:Std_ToggleBottomPanels.svg|16px]] Toggle Bottom Panels}} option from the menu.
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Std_ToggleBottomPanels.svg|16px]] Toggle Bottom Panels}} button in the [[Status_Bar|Status Bar]] context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Ctrl}} + {{KEY|O}}.


